WEBVTT

00:15:27.757 --> 00:15:32.788
And so, as your home
is filled with equipment that's digital,

00:15:32.812 --> 00:15:34.302
there will have to be rules --

00:15:34.326 --> 00:15:36.982
otherwise people stop using this stuff.

00:15:37.006 --> 00:15:39.172
And remember, the marketplace
is still there.

00:15:39.196 --> 00:15:44.359
If these things aren't able to resolve

00:15:44.383 --> 00:15:46.309
some of these downsides,

00:15:46.333 --> 00:15:49.550
the usage will go down.

00:15:49.942 --> 00:15:53.046
CA: So your view is that fundamentally,
these are fixable problems

00:15:53.070 --> 00:15:55.601
that we need to invent
our way out of them.

00:15:55.625 --> 00:15:58.180
Is there a case for people
in the tech industry,

00:15:58.204 --> 00:15:59.505
like yourself and others,

00:15:59.529 --> 00:16:04.069
to sort of offer services,
some kind of grand council of elders